    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a Chinese dynastic culture, style, and period dating 1115 to 1234, an empire formed by the Tungus Juchen (or Jurchen) tribes of Manchuria. The empire covered much of Inner Asia and all of present-day North China.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
